  "targetLanguage": "HTML",
  "instruction": "Write an HTML5 head combining charset, viewport, description, canonical link, and a referrer policy meta tag.",
  "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Release notes for version 5.0 of the analytics platform.\" />\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://example.com/releases/5-0\" />\n    <meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" />\n    <title>Analytics 5.0 release notes</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>Analytics 5.0 release notes</h1>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>",
